Populated places (points) map for Comoros Union

Source: R/data.R
ppl.Rd

Populated places (points) map for Comoros Union

ppl

Format

A SpatialPointsDataFrame with 144 features:

osm_id

Open Street Map identifier

is_in

Where is this place located?

source

Source of populated place information

place

Type of populated place

population

Population number

name

Name of populated place

Source

https://data.humdata.org/dataset/hotosm_com_populated_places

Examples

ppl
